title: Severe traffic delays in Kent
text:
Severe traffic delays in Kent this morning as the knock-on delays of Operation Stack cause major problems.
On the M20, Kent northbound there is disruption between J9 for the A20, Ashford, and J8 for Leeds Castle.
Also on the M20, Kent northbound there are long delays between J2 for the A20 and the M25.
On the M20 Kent southbound there is disruption between J8 for Leeds Castle and J11.
On the M2, Kent eastbound, there is congestion around J7.
